        <div class="company-info">
            <h2 >About Mindtree</h2>
            <p>
               <strong> Mindtree</strong> is a global technology consulting and services company headquartered in Bangalore, India. Founded in <strong>1999 by a group of seven entrepreneurs—Krishnan, Subroto Bagchi</strong>, and others—Mindtree initially emerged as a startup offering IT services and solutions to companies worldwide. Over the years, it has grown into one of the leading digital transformation and technology consulting firms.
                <br><br>

                Mindtree focuses on providing services like IT consulting, application development, enterprise solutions, digital transformation, cloud, data analytics, cybersecurity, and quality assurance. Its clients come from various industries, including banking, insurance, retail, manufacturing, and high-tech. The company's offerings are designed to help organizations embrace the future of technology, leveraging cutting-edge innovations to enhance business processes and operations.
                <br><br>
                
                The company started with a vision to create a culture that valued creativity, collaboration, and technical expertise. Mindtree's philosophy is rooted in its core values of customer-centricity, innovation, and commitment to delivering value, which has helped the company build long-term relationships with clients. Over the years, Mindtree has established a reputation for driving business transformation through its focus on high-quality IT services and a strong culture of continuous learning.
                <br><br>
                
                Mindtree went public in 2007, listing its shares on the Bombay Stock Exchange and the National Stock Exchange of India. Its success story continued with a series of acquisitions and expansions, enhancing its global presence. In 2019, the company was acquired by L&T Group, one of India's largest conglomerates, which enabled it to scale up its capabilities and accelerate growth.
                <br><br>
                
                The current CEO of Mindtree is <strong>Debashis Chatterjee</strong>, who assumed the position in 2020. Under his leadership, Mindtree has focused on expanding its service offerings, strengthening its position in the digital space, and fostering innovation through collaborations with global technology partners. With a global workforce of over 28,000 employees across multiple countries, Mindtree continues to be a key player in the IT services industry, driving digital transformation and delivering cutting-edge solutions to clients worldwide.
                
            </p>
                
            
            
        </div>
